Fresh fish!

32
00:02:38,596 --> 00:02:41,396
Let's spit on our hands
and get to work.

33
00:02:41,477 --> 00:02:42,837
It's late, Maury.

34
00:02:42,917 --> 00:02:44,277
Not anymore, Lil.

35
00:02:44,358 --> 00:02:45,638
It's early.

36
