00:03:05,483 --> 00:03:07,684
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

41
00:03:11,925 --> 00:03:15,766
- Author!
- Author!

42
00:03:16,766 --> 00:03:18,967
- Author!
- Author!

43
00:03:19,047 --> 00:03:20,527
- Author!
- Author!

44
